01:26:23,070 --> 01:26:25,430
我跑左邊     好
- I go left.   - Alright.

830
01:26:25,630 --> 01:26:29,000
厄本，跟傑克森對調，而你待在後面
Upham, switch off with Jackson and you linger in the rear.

831
01:26:30,670 --> 01:26:34,510
我們向前猛攻，迫使他換子彈
We advance and keep pressure on him 'til he has to change out his barrels.

832
01:26:36,350 --> 01:26:38,280
然後就扔手榴彈
We should be able to hit them from grenade range.

833
01:26:38,510 --> 01:26:42,380
也許我該跑中間     你那種跑法嗎，不用了
- Maybe I should go up the middle?   - The way you run? I don't think so.

834
01:26:42,580 --> 01:26:46,850
也許我該跑左邊     也許你該閉嘴
- Maybe I should go left,sir.   - Maybe you should shut up!

835
01:26:47,060 --> 01:26:49,920
萊賓，儘管開火
Reiben, base of fire.

836
01:26:58,170 --> 01:27:00,860
把彈藥帶在身邊
Mags and clips where you can reach them

837
01:27:01,070 --> 01:27:03,800
負責主攻的多帶些手榴彈
and extra grenades for the base runners.

838
01:28:28,860 --> 01:28:31,720
山上安全了，幹掉了四個     厄本
- Hill's clear. Four down and dead!   - Upham!

839
01:28:31,930 --> 01:28:35,520
收拾裝備帶上來，我們需要水和藥物
Grab the gear and get up here! We need water and extra dressing.

840
01:28:35,730 --> 01:28:40,530
從藥包裡把嗎啡拿出來
Get the morphine out of the medical kit!

841
01:28:52,110 --> 01:28:54,340
混蛋     撒上磺胺粉
- Son of a bitch!   - Get some sulfa on there.

842
01:28:54,550 --> 01:28:56,680
把我的腿抬高     行了
- Move my legs up.   - I got them.

843
01:28:56,890 --> 01:28:58,550
快倒磺胺粉     聽我說
- Pour sulfa.   - Listen to my voice.

844
01:28:58,750 --> 01:29:00,920
你會沒事的，醫師
You're going to be alright, Doc.

845
01:29:02,590 --> 01:29:04,680
沒事的，很快就能上醫療船
You're fine. You're going on a hospital ship.

846
01:29:04,890 --> 01:29:07,560
倒多一點     把腿抬起
- More sulfa!   - Move my legs up.

847
01:29:07,760 --> 01:29:10,600
把腿抬高     行了
- Put my legs up.   - I've got them.

848
01:29:10,800 --> 01:29:12,730
你會沒事的     沒事，醫生
- You're going to be OK.   - It's alright, Doc.

849
01:29:12,940 --> 01:29:15,870
厄本，把水壺給我     快
- Upham, give me your canteen!   - Come on.

850
01:29:16,070 --> 01:29:20,300
我們會帶你離開的     壓著傷口
- We're going to get you out of here.   - Put some pressure on it.

851
01:29:20,510 --> 01:29:22,670
我中彈了嗎，傷勢怎麼樣     給他注射嗎啡
- Am I shot? How does it look?   - Give him some morphine.

852
01:29:22,880 --> 01:29:26,870
傷勢怎麼樣     你會沒事的
- How does it look?   - You're going to be OK.

853
01:29:27,120 --> 01:29:28,670
要注射嗎啡了
Here comes the morphine.

854
01:29:29,480 --> 01:29:32,390
被射中脊椎了嗎
Am I shot in the spine?

855
01:29:33,190 --> 01:29:35,490
沒事的     是不是射中脊椎
- You're OK.   - Am I shot in the spine?

856
01:29:35,690 --> 01:29:37,680
抬起他     把他翻過去
- Lift him up.   - Move him over.

857
01:29:37,930 --> 01:29:40,550
壓著傷口     輕點
- Put some pressure on.   - Easy, easy.

858
01:29:44,300 --> 01:29:47,330
沒事的，醫生
It's OK, Doc. It's alright.

859
01:29:47,540 --> 01:29:51,530
韋德，子彈穿了出去，你背後有個彈孔
Wade, you've got an exit wound. It's in the small of your back.

860
01:29:51,770 --> 01:29:55,170
那個洞有多大     像橡果那麼大
- How big is the hole?   - It's about the size of an acorn.

861
01:29:55,380 --> 01:29:57,810
好了     放下他
- It's fine.   - Put him back.

862
01:30:00,050 --> 01:30:04,140
壓住傷口
Put some pressure on it. Put some pressure on it.

863
01:30:04,350 --> 01:30:06,950
壓住傷口
Put some pressure on it!

864
01:30:08,360 --> 01:30:09,920
用力一點
Put some more pressure on it.

865
01:30:11,590 --> 01:30:13,720
還有更嚴重的傷口嗎
Is there anything bleeding worse than the others?

866
01:30:13,930 --> 01:30:17,090
有，這裡，知道在哪裡嗎，這裡
Yeah, right here. Do you know what it is? Right here.

867
01:30:17,300 --> 01:30:20,740
我把你的手放到上面     我們正壓著傷口
- I'll put your hand on it.   - We got some pressure on there.

868
01:30:20,970 --> 01:30:22,800
就是這裡
That's the one.

869
01:30:23,010 --> 01:30:27,070
天啊，那是我的肝臟
Oh, my God! My liver! It's my liver!

870
01:30:28,210 --> 01:30:30,510
教我們該怎麼救你
Tell us what to do. Tell us how to fix you.

871
01:30:30,710 --> 01:30:33,340
我們該怎麼辦，告訴我們
What can we do? Tell us what to do.

872
01:30:35,380 --> 01:30:39,680
給我一點嗎啡
I could use a little morphine.

873
01:30:40,490 --> 01:30:43,010
多一點嗎啡
More morphine, sir.

874
01:30:43,230 --> 01:30:46,160
好的
OK. OK.

875
01:30:48,300 --> 01:30:51,660
什麼     給他注射
- Sir? What?   - Give it to him.

876
01:30:53,340 --> 01:30:55,430
給他注射
Give it to him.

877
01:30:59,140 --> 01:31:04,010
我不想死     韋德，我們正在注射
- I don't want to die!   - Here you go, Wade. Here it comes.

878
01:31:08,820 --> 01:31:10,610
再注射一劑
Give him another one.

879
01:31:17,830 --> 01:31:19,920
媽媽
Mama...

880
01:31:21,660 --> 01:31:23,690
媽媽
Mama.

881
01:31:23,900 --> 01:31:27,530
我想回家
I want to go home, I want go home.

882
01:31:28,470 --> 01:31:31,270
媽媽
Mama, Mama, Mama...

883
01:31:31,470 --> 01:31:37,000
媽媽
Mama, Mama, Mama, Mama...

884
01:32:17,290 --> 01:32:19,410
萊賓，抓住他
Reiben, hold him!

885
01:32:39,670 --> 01:32:41,370
等一下
Not yet!

886
01:32:43,580 --> 01:32:46,550
先叫他替韋德挖個墳墓
First make him mark and cover Wade's body for Grave Detail.

887
01:32:48,180 --> 01:32:51,310
也替那些傘兵挖個墳墓
Same thing for the paratroopers down there.

888
01:32:51,520 --> 01:32:54,050
拿走他的裝備，查問他
Strip that stuff off him. Check him for intelligence.

889
01:32:54,260 --> 01:32:58,220
問這混蛋，韋德是不是他殺的，快問
Ask this piece of shit if he shot Wade! Ask him!

890
01:32:58,460 --> 01:32:59,890
有用嗎     有
- Does it matter?   - It does!

891
01:33:03,570 --> 01:33:06,360
閉上你的臭嘴
Shut up with that filthy pig Latin.

892
01:33:08,240 --> 01:33:11,210
傑克森，你中彈了嗎
Jackson, are you hit?

893
01:33:14,210 --> 01:33:15,470
只是擦傷而已
It just skinned the arm.

894
01:33:15,680 --> 01:33:21,080
把傷口處理好，你和中士留意周圍
Get it cleaned and dressed. You and Sarge watch the perimeter.

895
01:33:23,220 --> 01:33:27,310
他求我們別殺他     厄本，我不管他說什麼
- He says, "Please don't shoot."   - I don't care what he says, Upham.

896
01:33:28,620 --> 01:33:31,520
長官，你要讓他們殺他嗎
Sir? Sir, are you going to let them kill him?

897
01:33:32,590 --> 01:33:36,860
這是不對的     那你去幫他埋屍體
- This is not right, sir.   - You can help him with the bodies.

898
01:33:39,230 --> 01:33:41,330
這是什麼一回事
What is happening?

899
01:35:31,480 --> 01:35:34,540
美國人
American.

900
01:35:34,750 --> 01:35:36,650
我喜歡美國人
I like American.

901
01:35:44,030 --> 01:35:46,550
輪船威裡
Steamboat Willie.

902
01:35:46,760 --> 01:35:51,130
輪船威裡     輪船威裡，美國人
- Steamboat Willie.   - Steamboat Willie. American.

903
01:36:02,410 --> 01:36:08,280
他說他還沒完成     那是你的想法，來吧
- He says he's not finished.   - That's what you think. Come on.

904
01:36:16,320 --> 01:36:20,120
求求你，我喜歡美國人
Please! I like America!

905
01:36:21,360 --> 01:36:23,330
美國什麼都好
Fancy schmancy! What a cinch!

906
01:36:23,570 --> 01:36:27,000
美國什麼都有
Go fly a kite! Cat got your tongue! Cool beans!

907
01:36:30,740 --> 01:36:33,670
貝蒂小姐，好性感
Betty Boop! What a dish.

908
01:36:33,910 --> 01:36:35,970
貝蒂嘉寶，腿很美
Betty Grable. Nice gams.

909
01:36:43,080 --> 01:36:45,850
我說你看到嗎
I say can you see

910
01:36:46,050 --> 01:36:48,990
我說你看到嗎
I say can you see

911
01:36:49,190 --> 01:36:51,280
我說
