912
01:36:58,200 --> 01:36:59,860
去你的希特勒
Fuck Hitler.

913
01:37:01,870 --> 01:37:03,860
去你的希特勒
Fuck Hitler!

914
01:37:12,650 --> 01:37:16,810
長官，他說他替韋德的死難過
Sir, he says he's sorry about Wade. He says he's sorry about Wade.

915
01:37:17,020 --> 01:37:18,650
上尉
Captain!

916
01:37:18,850 --> 01:37:22,380
上尉，你也知道這樣做不對
Captain, this isn't right. You know this.

917
01:37:22,590 --> 01:37:27,390
他是戰俘，他已經投降了
He's a prisoner. He surrendered. He surrendered, sir!

918
01:37:37,810 --> 01:37:39,430
告訴他
Tell him...

919
01:37:41,740 --> 01:37:46,610
朝那方向走一千步，然後脫掉蒙眼布
to march 1,000 paces in that direction.Then he can take off the blindfold.

920
01:37:46,820 --> 01:37:49,480
向首個遇到的盟軍自首
He turns himself in to the first Allied patrol.

921
01:37:49,680 --> 01:37:51,280
你在說笑嗎，放他走
Are you kidding? We're letting him go?

922
01:37:51,490 --> 01:37:55,180
萊賓，他是戰俘，不能帶著他走
He's a POW, Reiben. We can't take him with us.

923
01:37:55,390 --> 01:37:59,990
我軍自會處置他     算他命大
- Our guys will pick him up.   - That was a close shave.

924
01:38:00,200 --> 01:38:02,160
真幸運
Lucky Strikes.

925
01:38:06,030 --> 01:38:08,200
帶我去看球賽
Take me out to the ball game...

926
01:38:08,400 --> 01:38:14,100
萬一他被敵軍救回，又會回來作戰的
Only if he doesn't get picked up by his own and get thrown back into circulation.

927
01:38:15,640 --> 01:38:19,550
上尉，你白白放過了敵人     簡直白癡
- Captain, you just let the enemy go.   - This is such bullshit.

928
01:38:19,780 --> 01:38:23,580
沒錯     白癡，這是白癡嗎
- You all got that right.   - Bullshit? This is bullshit?

929
01:38:23,790 --> 01:38:26,350
難道可以射殺戰俘嗎，這樣是有違軍法的
Shooting a prisoner is OK? It's against the rules!

930
01:38:26,550 --> 01:38:30,960
軍法跟你的新朋友一起走了
The goddam rules just walked off with your new friend.

931
01:38:32,460 --> 01:38:35,830
上尉，這樣做是對的吧
But I guess that was the decent thing to do, Captain?

932
01:38:43,470 --> 01:38:45,940
收拾東西，出發吧
Get your gear. Let's go.

933
01:38:48,340 --> 01:38:50,610
你們聽到了，收拾東西
You heard him. Gear up.

934
01:38:51,680 --> 01:38:54,940
上尉剛下了命令     是的
- The Captain just gave you an order.   - Yeah.

935
01:38:55,150 --> 01:38:58,880
就像他下令攻下機槍台一樣，真是大英雄
Like the one he gave to take this machine gun. That was a real doozy.

936
01:38:59,090 --> 01:39:00,520
你太過分了
You're out of line!

937
01:39:00,760 --> 01:39:03,690
他命令我們拿下這裡真是英明
That was one hell of a call coming to take this nest,

938
01:39:03,890 --> 01:39:06,830
