but what the hell, we only lost one of our guys going for it.

939
01:39:07,030 --> 01:39:10,290
瑞恩媽媽一定很高興，知道她兒子的性命
I hope Mama Ryan's really happy knowing that little Jimmy's life

940
01:39:10,500 --> 01:39:12,860
比我們兩位隊友的還重要
was more important than two of our guys!

941
01:39:13,070 --> 01:39:16,060
但我們還沒找到他吧
But then, we haven't found them, have we?

942
01:39:17,840 --> 01:39:19,270
你     放開我
- Hey...   - Get off me!

943
01:39:19,470 --> 01:39:21,840
萊賓，起來
Reiben, get up.

944
01:39:23,110 --> 01:39:26,480
拿起東西，入列
Gear up. Fall in.

945
01:39:31,190 --> 01:39:33,620
