I'm done with this mission.

946
01:39:38,490 --> 01:39:40,980
等等
Hey! Hey!

947
01:39:41,860 --> 01:39:43,850
長官     你不能一走了之
- Sir...   - Don't you walk away from your captain!

948
01:39:44,100 --> 01:39:46,290
萊賓，給我回來     不
- Reiben, get back in line!   - No, sir.

949
01:39:46,500 --> 01:39:49,200
我寧可坐牢也不想繼續了
I'll spend the rest of my life in the stockade rather than go on.

950
01:39:49,400 --> 01:39:51,800
我說最後一遍     上尉
- I'm not going to ask you again.   - Captain!

951
01:39:52,010 --> 01:39:54,410
白癡     入列
