952
01:39:54,610 --> 01:39:57,840
你要因為瑞恩而殺我嗎     不，是因為我討厭你
- Are you going to shoot me over Ryan?   - No, because I don't like you.

953
01:39:58,050 --> 01:40:00,240
他想走就讓他走吧
If he wants to go, just let him go!

954
01:40:00,450 --> 01:40:03,680
你不管嗎，上尉，你看到了嗎
Are you letting this happen? Captain! You see this?

955
01:40:03,890 --> 01:40:06,820
上尉，瑞恩已經死了
Captain. Sir, Ryan's dead.

956
01:40:07,060 --> 01:40:09,420
白癡     這裡情況不妙
- Bullshit!   - We have a situation here.

957
01:40:09,620 --> 01:40:12,020
我有很強的第六感
I have a sixth sense. I know it in my bones.

958
01:40:12,230 --> 01:40:14,890
你不殺德軍卻要殺我嗎
We didn't kill the Kraut. Now you're going to shoot me.

959
01:40:15,100 --> 01:40:17,390
他比你好     下手吧
- He's better than you.   - Just do it!

960
01:40:17,600 --> 01:40:22,000
打我的腿     我要打你的大嘴巴
- Put one in my leg...   - I'll shoot you in your big mouth!

961
01:40:22,200 --> 01:40:23,860
廢話少說，開槍吧
Put your money where your mouth is and do it!

962
01:40:24,070 --> 01:40:26,700
你總是那麼多話說
You don't know how to shut up.

963
01:40:26,910 --> 01:40:31,500
上尉，求求你     賭金有多少了
- Captain, please!   - What's the pool on me up to?

964
01:40:31,710 --> 01:40:35,010
你是個懦弱的混蛋     中士，我在等你開槍
- You are a coward son of a bitch!   - I'm waiting, Sarge.

965
01:40:35,220 --> 01:40:38,280
賭金累積到有多少了
What's the pool on me up to right now?

966
01:40:38,490 --> 01:40:40,780
有多少了
What's it up to?

967
01:40:40,990 --> 01:40:43,820
三百塊嗎
What is it? 300 dollars, is that it?

968
01:40:44,030 --> 01:40:46,260
我是個老師
I'm a schoolteacher.

969
01:40:49,830 --> 01:40:53,100
我教英文作文
I teach English Composition...

970
01:40:53,300 --> 01:40:55,670
在賓夕法尼亞州一個叫艾德里的小鎮
in this little town called Addley, Pennsylvania.

971
01:40:55,870 --> 01:41:01,000
這十一年來我在湯瑪斯愛迪生高校任教
In the last 11 years, I've been at Thomas Alva Edison High School.

972
01:41:03,140 --> 01:41:07,480
在春季我是棒球教練
I was the coach of the baseball team in the springtime.

973
01:41:09,520 --> 01:41:11,250
我真該死
I'll be doggone.

974
01:41:11,450 --> 01:41:14,890
我在家鄉告訴人家我的職業時
Back home, when I tell people what I do for a living

975
01:41:15,120 --> 01:41:18,790
他們覺得“一看就知道”
they think, "Well, that figures."

976
01:41:19,860 --> 01:41:23,590
但到了這裡
But over here, it's...

977
01:41:23,800 --> 01:41:28,100
卻成為了一個大秘密
a big, big mystery.

978
01:41:29,370 --> 01:41:33,270
我想我變了一點
So, I guess I've changed some.

979
01:41:34,640 --> 01:41:37,810
有時我想我改變了很多
Sometimes I wonder if I've changed so much

980
01:41:38,010 --> 01:41:42,070
回家後也許妻子會不認得我
my wife is even going to recognise me whenever I get back to her...

981
01:41:43,990 --> 01:41:46,850
或許我不能向她
and how I'll ever be able to...

982
01:41:49,090 --> 01:41:51,990
訴說像今天這種事情
tell her about days like today.

983
01:41:54,300 --> 01:41:57,390
瑞恩
Ryan...

984
01:41:57,600 --> 01:42:01,090
我對瑞恩一無所知，我才不管
I don't know anything about Ryan. I don't care.

985
01:42:01,340 --> 01:42:03,300
他跟我毫無關係，那只是個名字
He means nothing to me, it's just a name,

986
01:42:03,540 --> 01:42:10,740
但要是到蘭姆勒帶他回家
but if going to Ramelle and finding him so he can go home,

987
01:42:10,950 --> 01:42:14,750
能讓我回到妻子身邊
if that earns me the right to get back to my wife, then...

988
01:42:14,950 --> 01:42:17,940
我會接下這項任務
...then that's my mission.

989
01:42:19,090 --> 01:42:24,490
你想退出，重返戰場嗎
You want to leave? You want to go off and fight the war?

990
01:42:26,730 --> 01:42:29,360
沒關係
Alright.

991
01:42:29,560 --> 01:42:36,490
我不會阻止你，我甚至會替你申請
Alright, I won't stop you. I'll even put in the paperwork.

992
01:42:36,740 --> 01:42:41,510
我只知道我多殺一人便離家越遠
I just know that with every man I kill, the farther away from home I feel.

993
01:44:06,290 --> 01:44:11,230
∮ 昔日的回憶湧現 ∮
by memories of days gone by

994
01:44:13,130 --> 01:44:18,000
∮ 孤獨中你嘲弄我 ∮
In my solitude you taunt me

995
01:44:18,210 --> 01:44:22,970
∮ 勾起不死的記憶 ∮
with memories that never die

996
01:44:23,180 --> 01:44:28,010
∮ 我坐在椅上滿懷絕望 ∮
I sit in my chair filled with despair

997
01:44:28,220 --> 01:44:33,180
∮ 比任何人都要哀傷 ∮
There's no one could be so sad

998
01:44:33,420 --> 01:44:37,820
∮ 看著坐著的地方盡是陰霾 ∮
With gloom everywhere I sit and I stare

999
01:44:38,030 --> 01:44:42,520
∮ 我很快就會瘋掉 ∮
I know that I'll soon go mad

1000
01:44:51,740 --> 01:44:53,830
有坦克，躲好
Half-track! Cover!

1001
01:45:09,590 --> 01:45:13,490
是誰開槍
Who's doing the shooting? Who's doing the shooting?

1002
01:45:33,980 --> 01:45:36,420
準備行動，攻擊左邊
Get ready to move. Take their left flank!

1003
01:45:36,650 --> 01:45:38,850
小心點，以防有餘兵
Hold on and make sure they're down.

1004
01:46:00,370 --> 01:46:03,500
我們是101師，現在出來
101st! We're coming out!

1005
01:46:10,480 --> 01:46:13,420
裝甲兵第二師
That was a recon. element, 2nd SS.

1006
01:46:14,820 --> 01:46:18,280
我們正在等待情報，一定是他們了
We've been expecting a probe. That must have been it.

1007
01:46:20,190 --> 01:46:23,490
第二突擊隊C連米勒上尉
Captain Miller, Charlie Company, 2nd Rangers.

1008
01:46:23,700 --> 01:46:25,790
501師E連漢德森下士
Corporal Henderson, Easy Company, 501st.

1009
01:46:26,000 --> 01:46:29,830
506團第一隊瑞恩     506團第三隊托恩比
- Ryan, First of 506th.   - Toynbee, Third of 506th.

1010
01:46:30,040 --> 01:46:35,770
詹姆斯·法蘭西斯·瑞恩     對，你怎麼會知道
- James Francis Ryan?   - Yes,sir.How did you guess that?

1011
01:46:46,550 --> 01:46:52,890
看來敵方攻勢猛烈     對，是小組部隊的進攻
- Looks like you got hit pretty hard.   - Yes,sir.Small unit action.

1012
01:46:55,260 --> 01:46:59,630
他們的88毫米炮威力強勁
They came in and beat the hell out of us with 88s.

1013
01:47:05,140 --> 01:47:08,540
要是你們就是救兵，我可要投訴
Tell you what. If you're our relief, I'm going to file a complaint.

1014
01:47:08,780 --> 01:47:11,200
我不會怪你
I wouldn't blame you.

1015
01:47:11,440 --> 01:47:14,640
誰是你的指揮官
Who's your CO?

1016
01:47:14,850 --> 01:47:17,480
原本是簡甯斯上尉
It would've been Captain Jennings.

1017
01:47:17,690 --> 01:47:20,800
但下士已是這兒的最高級軍官了
I'm afraid the best we can muster up now is a corporal.

1018
01:47:22,250 --> 01:47:25,230
那你們為什麼來這裡
So what are you guys all about?

1019
01:47:25,460 --> 01:47:28,950
我們為他而來，瑞恩
We're here for him. Ryan.

1020
01:47:29,200 --> 01:47:31,030
我
Me, sir?

1021
01:47:39,970 --> 01:47:43,210
你是愛阿華州的詹姆斯·法蘭西斯·瑞恩吧
James Francis Ryan of lowa?

1022
01:47:43,410 --> 01:47:48,530
對，愛阿華州佩頓市，這是怎麼回事
Yes, sir. Peyton,Iowa, that's correct. What is this about?

1023
01:47:50,580 --> 01:47:53,280
你兄長陣亡了
Your brothers were killed in combat.

1024
01:48:00,250 --> 01:48:02,200
哪一個
Which ones?

1025
01:48:04,770 --> 01:48:07,060
全部
All of them.

1026
01:48:15,080 --> 01:48:17,690
真的嗎
On the level?

1027
01:48:19,050 --> 01:48:22,410
恐怕是真的
Yeah, I'm afraid so.

1028
01:48:23,680 --> 01:48:25,620
大概要一段時間才能接受
You might want to take some time with this.

1029
01:48:25,850 --> 01:48:29,110
要是你想到什麼地方
If there's someplace you want to go and...

1030
01:48:37,890 --> 01:48:40,730
是怎麼回事     瑞恩的兄弟去世了
- What's this all about?   - Ryan lost his brothers.

1031
01:48:40,940 --> 01:48:43,960
哪一個     全部
- Which one?   - All of them.

1032
01:48:52,280 --> 01:48:54,970
你們專程跑來告訴我嗎
You came all the way out here to tell me that?

1033
01:48:57,350 --> 01:49:00,580
你要回家
You're going home.

1034
01:49:00,790 --> 01:49:03,520
我們奉命帶你回去
Our orders are to bring you back.

1035
01:49:07,020 --> 01:49:09,220
帶我回去
Bring me back?

1036
01:49:10,800 --> 01:49:15,590
下士，我不是想令你人手短缺，但這是命令
Corporal,I don't mean to leave you more short-handed,but orders are orders.

1037
01:49:15,790 --> 01:49:18,420
想跟什麼人聯絡嗎
Any communications about when you will be relieved?

1038
01:49:18,630 --> 01:49:21,570
我們也不知道南方的情況
We can't tell. We don't know what's happening south of us.

1039
01:49:21,810 --> 01:49:25,130
但我的命令不許我擅離職守
My orders don't include me abandoning my post.

1040
01:49:25,340 --> 01:49:27,970
我知道，但情況有變
I understand that, but this changes things.

1041
01:49:28,180 --> 01:49:30,450
我不認同
I don't see that it does, sir.

1042
01:49:32,090 --> 01:49:35,670
這是美軍參謀長的命令
The Chief of Staff for the US Army says it does.

1043
01:49:35,880 --> 01:49:38,090
我們奉命死守這座橋
Our orders are to hold this bridge at all costs.

1044
01:49:38,290 --> 01:49:41,390
我方戰機已經把麥德里特河的所有橋樑炸斷
Our planes in the 82nd have taken out every bridge across the Merderet,

1045
01:49:41,600 --> 01:49:44,380
除了瓦隆尼和這裡兩處
with the exception of two: one at Valognes and this one.

1046
01:49:44,590 --> 01:49:47,080
要是給德軍拿下我們就要退守
If the Germans take it, we'll have to displace.

1047
01:49:47,330 --> 01:49:52,230
部隊的任務是一回事，但你要離開了
Private.It's one thing that your outfit wants to stay,but your party's over here.

1048
01:49:52,460 --> 01:49:54,330
援軍到達前我不能離開
I can't leave before the reinforcements are here.

1049
01:49:54,530 --> 01:49:56,930
三分鐘內收拾行裝
You've got three minutes to get your gear.

1050
01:49:57,130 --> 01:50:00,880
那他們怎麼辦     混蛋
- What about them,there's barely...   - Hey,asshole!

1051
01:50:01,080 --> 01:50:04,970
我們兩位隊友已經為你送命
Two of our guys already died trying to find you.

1052
01:50:10,490 --> 01:50:13,420
真的嗎     是的
- Sir?   - That's right.

1053
01:50:22,990 --> 01:50:27,340
他們叫什麼名字     艾文·韋德和艾德林·卡帕佐
- What were their names?   - Irwin Wade and Adrian Caparzo.

1054
01:50:29,510 --> 01:50:31,020
韋德和誰
Wade and?

1055
01:50:32,340 --> 01:50:34,070
卡帕佐
Caparzo.

1056
01:50:46,380 --> 01:50:48,730
沒有理由要這樣
It doesn't make any sense.

1057
01:50:50,860 --> 01:50:55,000
這樣沒道理，我有什麼資格離開
It doesn't make any sense, sir. Why do I deserve to go?

1058
01:50:55,200 --> 01:50:58,070
為什麼不是他們，他們也同樣努力
Why not any of these guys? They all fought just as hard as me.

1059
01:51:03,030 --> 01:51:06,140
你死後傳訊員就要跟
Is that what they're supposed to tell your mother

1060
01:51:06,350 --> 01:51:09,400
你母親這樣說嗎
when they send her another folded American flag?

1061
01:51:16,660 --> 01:51:19,910
跟她說你在這裡找到我
Tell her that when you found me I was here,

1062
01:51:20,120 --> 01:51:22,880
我要跟軍中其他兄弟在一起
and I was with the only brothers that I have left,

1063
01:51:23,090 --> 01:51:27,180
我怎樣也不會離棄他們
and that there was no way I was going to desert them.

1064
01:51:27,390 --> 01:51:32,560
她應該會明白，我不會離開這座橋
I think she'll understand that. There's no way I'm leaving this bridge.

1065
01:52:15,610 --> 01:52:17,670
現在怎麼辦
What are your orders?

1066
01:52:19,480 --> 01:52:23,480
中士，我們進入了一個奇異的國度
Sergeant, we have crossed some strange boundary here.

1067
01:52:23,720 --> 01:52:26,240
一切都異乎尋常
Our world has taken a turn for the surreal.

1068
01:52:26,480 --> 01:52:29,880
但問題始終要解決
Clearly, but the question still stands.

1069
01:52:30,090 --> 01:52:33,960
我不知道，你覺得怎樣
I don't know. What do you think?

1070
01:52:34,160 --> 01:52:36,650
你不會想知道
You don't want to know what I think.

1071
01:52:38,730 --> 01:52:40,890
不，我想知道
No, Mike, I do.

1072
01:52:44,070 --> 01:52:47,970
我一方面同意他的說法他有什麼資格
Part of me thinks the kid's right. What's he done to deserve this?

1073
01:52:48,170 --> 01:52:52,180
他既然想留下來，我們就乾脆回去
If he wants to stay here, fine. Let's leave him and go home.

1074
01:52:53,180 --> 01:52:55,040
是的
Yeah.

1075
01:52:55,250 --> 01:53:00,380
但我還有一個想法，要是我們也留下來
But another part of me thinks, "What if by some miracle we stay"

1076
01:53:00,580 --> 01:53:03,350
會締造什麼奇跡呢
"and actually make it out of here?"

1077
01:53:03,550 --> 01:53:07,460
有天我們回想此事
Some day we might look back on this and decide that

1078
01:53:07,690 --> 01:53:12,150
也許會覺得在這場混帳戰爭中
saving Private Ryan was the one decent thing we pulled out of

1079
01:53:12,400 --> 01:53:17,160
拯救瑞恩是唯一的好事
this whole godawful, shitty mess.

1080
01:53:17,370 --> 01:53:24,170
這是我的想法，上尉，如你所言
That's what I was thinking, sir. Like you said, Captain.

1081
01:53:25,680 --> 01:53:30,840
我們會留下來一起為團聚戰鬥
We do that, we all earn the right to go home.

1082
01:53:33,650 --> 01:53:35,780
兄弟
Oh, brother...

1083
01:53:38,420 --> 01:53:41,360
只有這些武器
This is everything.

1084
01:53:41,560 --> 01:53:47,690
23毫米機槍、17枚手榴彈、11個霍金斯地雷
You've got the.230 calibre machine guns, 17 grenades, 11 Hawkins mines.

1085
01:53:47,900 --> 01:53:51,100
你有兩支火箭筒，但只能發射八次
You've got two bazookas, but they've only got eight rounds left.

1086
01:53:51,300 --> 01:53:53,430
還有各式小手槍
And assorted small arms.

1087
01:53:53,640 --> 01:53:56,870
本來有60毫米迫擊炮，但已損毀
We had a.60 mortar, but an arty round took it out.

1088
01:53:57,070 --> 01:53:59,700
敵軍坦克壓過來我們吐口水攻擊好了
Might as well be spit wads if they roll on us with tanks.

1089
01:53:59,910 --> 01:54:04,510
敵軍當然會動用坦克     你有什麼意見
- Which they're sure to do.   - What are you thinking, sir?

1090
01:54:04,720 --> 01:54:08,120
我提議進行夾擊
I'm thinking I'm going to whip around the flanks.

1091
01:54:12,460 --> 01:54:15,720
要把他們引到大街
Unless we can draw them up the main road between the buildings,

1092
01:54:15,930 --> 01:54:19,420
用瓦礫造一個瓶頸
where all the rubble makes a bit of a bottleneck

1093
01:54:19,660 --> 01:54:21,820
讓坦克無用武之地嗎     可以的話
- Disable him?   - If we can.

1094
01:54:22,030 --> 01:54:25,660
造個六十噸的路障，然後展開夾擊
Make a 60-tonne roadblock. Then we've got a fighting chance at her flanks.

1095
01:54:25,870 --> 01:54:28,000
好，分散他們，別讓他們集結
Good. Split them up, don't let them mass.

1096
01:54:28,210 --> 01:54:31,070
然後逐一擊破，再退回大橋
Hit them hard one-on-one, and fall back to the bridge.

1097
01:54:31,280 --> 01:54:35,610
下麵放一台機槍，另一台置於高處
Machine gun on the move down here, number two up high to piss on them.

1098
01:54:35,810 --> 01:54:40,270
計畫就是這樣，傑克森
That would be the idea. Jackson!

1099
01:54:40,520 --> 01:54:42,820
可以的話我想你去鐘樓
If we can, I'd like to get you up in that bell tower.

1100
01:54:43,020 --> 01:54:46,050
知道     我會給你安排幫手
- Yes, sir.   - I'll give you some company.

1101
01:54:46,290 --> 01:54:52,200
也好，還要30毫米狙擊槍和一千發子彈
Some company couldn't hurt. A.30 with about a 1,000 rounds would be OK.

1102
01:54:52,430 --> 01:54:54,360
派克，有工作給你
Parker, job opportunity.

1103
01:54:54,600 --> 01:54:56,360
這主意不錯
It's not the worst idea ever,

1104
01:54:56,570 --> 01:55:00,230
但勝負關鍵在於把坦克弄到街上讓我們夾擊
but everything depends on getting the tank down the road for us to knock out.

1105
01:55:00,440 --> 01:55:03,770
你有什麼計畫
How the hell do you plan on doing that?

1106
01:55:03,970 --> 01:55:06,640
他說得對，空降師的隊友剛說
He's right. As our colleague from Airborne pointed out

1107
01:55:06,840 --> 01:55:09,110
我們有的是口水
what we've got is a bunch of spit wads.

1108
01:55:09,310 --> 01:55:13,150
但把坦克引來後怎麼應付
How do we stop the tank if we get it to commit?

1109
01:55:13,350 --> 01:55:14,820
先用兔子引它追趕
Give it a rabbit to chase.

1110
01:55:15,850 --> 01:55:18,520
接著攻擊坦克的履帶
We could hit the tank in the tracks.

1111
01:55:19,190 --> 01:55:20,520
對，但用什麼攻擊
Yeah, but with what?

1112
01:55:22,990 --> 01:55:27,790
用粘附式炸彈     粘附式炸彈
- We could try a sticky bomb.   - Sticky bomb, sir?

1113
01:55:28,000 --> 01:55:30,160
是你編出來的吧
Sir, are you making that up?

1114
01:55:30,370 --> 01:55:33,560
不，你可以去翻翻作戰手冊
No, it's in the field manual. Check it out, if you want to.

1115
01:55:33,770 --> 01:55:37,900
手冊不知道在那裡，你儘管講解一下
We seem to be out of field manuals. Perhaps you could enlighten us.

1116
01:55:38,110 --> 01:55:41,340
有炸藥吧，黃色炸藥還是B成分炸藥
You have some demolition, don't you? TNT or Composition B?

1117
01:55:41,550 --> 01:55:45,740
很多，橋那裡的B炸藥，足以把橋炸斷兩次
Plenty. I've got that bridge wired with enough Composition B to blow it twice.

1118
01:55:45,950 --> 01:55:47,440
那拿一點出來
You can spare some, then.

1119
01:55:48,220 --> 01:55:54,590
用一隻軍襪裝滿炸藥
You take a standard GI sock, cram it full with Composition B,

1120
01:55:54,790 --> 01:55:59,790
再加進導火線，表面塗滿機油
and rig up a simple fuse. Then you coat the whole thing with axle grease.

1121
01:56:00,030 --> 01:56:03,400
炸彈扔出就能粘附於目標物
That way, when you throw it, it should stick.

1122
01:56:03,600 --> 01:56:06,070
有粘力，所以叫粘附式炸彈
It's a bomb that sticks. It's a sticky bomb.

1123
01:56:06,300 --> 01:56:10,210
有更好的方法，儘管說出來
Come up with a better way to knock the tracks off a tank, I'm all ears.

1124
01:56:10,440 --> 01:56:13,930
這主意不錯，我們要把襪子奉獻
This is good. Now we have to surrender our socks!

1125
01:56:28,460 --> 01:56:30,050
拉上去
Haul away.

1126
01:56:43,740 --> 01:56:48,110
選擇攻擊範圍，與鐘樓組成交叉火力網
Select the field of fire. Crossfire with the one in the bell tower.

1127
01:56:48,310 --> 01:56:50,250
我負責左方的地區
I can cover 12 to 9 from here.

1128
01:56:54,520 --> 01:56:57,010
慢慢來     拿到了
- Easy!   - I've got her!

1129
01:57:31,120 --> 01:57:33,060
這是地雷
Here are the mines.

1130
01:57:43,430 --> 01:57:46,200
要配置得當才行
For being the best we can do,

1131
01:57:46,400 --> 01:57:51,270
前面的機槍位置不太好
that forward machine gun is not in a terrible firing position.

1132
01:57:52,940 --> 01:57:55,380
應該放到這裡
And this position right here...

1133
01:57:57,610 --> 01:57:59,640
這是最後防線
This is the Alamo.

1134
01:57:59,880 --> 01:58:03,220
要是退到這裡，最後一個活人負責炸橋
They push us this far, the last man alive blows the bridge.

1135
01:58:03,420 --> 01:58:06,290
導火線能燒三十秒，告訴大家
We've only got a 30-second delay on the fuse, so tell everyone

1136
01:58:06,490 --> 01:58:11,120
點火後快逃，不然性命不保
that if you're last you'd better hurry or you'll not live long.

1137
01:58:12,000 --> 01:58:15,930
上尉，我有什麼任務
Captain? Where am I during all this?

1138
01:58:16,170 --> 01:58:20,500
留在我兩英尺之內，不許有異議
Never more than two feet away from me. And that's not negotiable.

1139
01:58:21,540 --> 01:58:24,940
跟我去拿彈藥
I'm going to get some ammo. Come on.

1140
01:58:27,080 --> 01:58:30,310
厄本，聽著     是的
- Hey, Upham, listen to me.   - Yes.

1141
01:58:30,510 --> 01:58:32,880
你在聽嗎     是的
- Are you listening?   - Yes.

1142
01:58:33,080 --> 01:58:36,710
我們會不斷東奔西跑
We're going to be displacing and falling back like crazy sons of bitches,

1143
01:58:36,920 --> 01:58:41,450
你要運送彈藥，隨傳隨到，不然我們就死定
so you've got to be Johnny-on-the-spot with the ammo,or we're dead.

1144
01:58:41,690 --> 01:58:43,090
你明白嗎     隨傳隨到
- Do you understand?   - Johnny-on-the-spot.

1145
01:58:43,290 --> 01:58:47,160
你沒事吧     沒事
- Yeah. Are you alright?   - Yeah.

1146
01:58:48,470 --> 01:58:51,590
我們從英國出發時也會分發香煙
When we shipped out of England we got cigarettes

1147
01:58:51,800 --> 01:58:54,570
我卻說“謝謝，我不抽煙”
and I said, "No, thank you. I don't smoke."

1148
01:58:59,180 --> 01:59:03,200
形勢很兇險吧     難以置信
- Quite a situation, huh?   - Unbelievable.

1149
01:59:03,450 --> 01:59:09,220
這差事混帳得不得了
Yeah. "Fucked-Up Beyond All Recognition", right?

1150
01:59:09,420 --> 01:59:11,890
沒錯
You've got that right.

1151
01:59:13,690 --> 01:59:17,020
“苦差”     是的
- "FUBAR"!   - Alright!

1152
01:59:17,230 --> 01:59:18,460
很痛
Ouch.

1153
01:59:18,660 --> 01:59:22,760
這可不是玩的
Yeah, well... It's going to be a real show, huh?

1154
01:59:22,970 --> 01:59:24,900
知道了
Yeah, OK.

1155
01:59:31,010 --> 01:59:32,870
放輕鬆
Take it easy.

1156
01:59:33,810 --> 01:59:35,440
“苦差”
"FUBAR."

1157
02:00:13,320 --> 02:00:16,380
是誰的歌聲
Who's that singing, sir?

1158
02:00:16,620 --> 02:00:18,550
艾迪斯·皮雅福
Edith Piaf.

1159
02:00:20,060 --> 02:00:23,320
她為什麼這麼傷心
What is she so upset about?

1160
02:00:23,530 --> 02:00:28,660
情人離異，但她的面容歷歷在目
Her lover left her, but she still sees his face everywhere she goes.

1161
02:00:29,930 --> 02:00:31,730
就是這樣
That would do it.

1162
02:01:00,930 --> 02:01:04,130
∮ 生命中就只有你 ∮
"Even life itself only represents you."

1163
02:01:07,040 --> 02:01:09,530
∮ 夢著你擁我入懷 ∮
"Sometimes I dream that I'm in your arms."

1164
02:01:09,770 --> 02:01:13,170
那是什麼，她曾經唱過     是副歌
- What was that? She sang it before.   - The chorus.

1165
02:01:13,410 --> 02:01:15,110
副歌
The chorus.

1166
02:01:15,310 --> 02:01:18,210
∮ 每當你耳語喃喃 ∮
"And you speak softly in my ear."

1167
02:01:19,880 --> 02:01:24,880
∮ 都讓我閉目靜聽 ∮
"And you say things that make my eyes close."

1168
02:01:27,220 --> 02:01:29,020
∮ 感覺美妙 ∮
"And I find that marvellous."

1169
02:01:29,230 --> 02:01:32,460
厄本
Again, Upham...

1170
02:01:32,660 --> 02:01:37,900
老實說，你使我莫名的興奮
...to be honest, I find myself curiously aroused by you.

1171
02:01:38,100 --> 02:01:39,590
棒極了
Marvellous.

1172
02:01:39,840 --> 02:01:43,570
這首歌很哀傷，開始時她唱著
It's a really melancholy song. At the beginning of the song she says:

1173
02:01:43,770 --> 02:01:49,580
∮ 你離去後，我就傷心絕望 ∮
"And then one day you left me and I've been desperate ever since."

1174
02:01:49,780 --> 02:01:52,750
∮ 漫天滿地，都是你的影子 ∮
"I see you all over the sky, I see you all over the earth."

1175
02:01:52,980 --> 02:01:56,380
再聽多幾首這種歌不用德軍開槍
Any more songs like this, the Krauts won't have to shoot me.

1176
02:01:56,620 --> 02:01:59,250
我就割脈自殺了
I'm just going to slit my own wrists.

1177
02:01:59,460 --> 02:02:01,890
厄本，你好奇怪
You're a strange bird, Upham.

1178
02:02:02,130 --> 02:02:04,060
對不起，是艾迪斯
I'm sorry. It's Edith, you know.

1179
02:02:04,290 --> 02:02:06,060
知道這首歌讓我想起什麼嗎
You know what that song reminds me of?

1180
02:02:06,260 --> 02:02:10,430
瑞雪太太在我出發前的一番話
Mrs. Rachel Troubowitz and what she said when I left for Basic.

1181
02:02:10,630 --> 02:02:13,070
說什麼     她說“別碰我”
- What?   - "Don't touch me?"

1182
02:02:13,300 --> 02:02:15,740
不，她是公寓管理員的妻子
No. She's our Super's wife.

1183
02:02:15,940 --> 02:02:22,370
她到我媽的店買衣服，胸圍有44EE
She comes into my mum's shop to try a few things. She's like a 44 Double E.

1184
02:02:22,610 --> 02:02:24,240
EE     好大呢
- Double E?   - They're massive.

1185
02:02:24,450 --> 02:02:25,810
是一對大胸脯
Those are big titties.

1186
02:02:26,020 --> 02:02:29,980
我騙她穿42D的衣服，我們在更衣室裡
I've got her convinced that she's a 42 D. So we're in the dressing room

1187
02:02:30,220 --> 02:02:34,180
她嘗試擠進那件絲帶束腰
and she tries to get into this side-cut,silk-ribboned,triple-panel girdle

1188
02:02:34,420 --> 02:02:36,760
