Everybody check your ammo!

1244
02:08:20,940 --> 02:08:25,600
萊賓，祝你好運     不用祝福，我生來幸運
- Good luck,Reiben!   - I don't need any luck,I was born lucky!

1245
02:08:38,660 --> 02:08:41,990
拿著五枚曳光彈     知道，照亮兩端
- One in five tracer.   - Yes, and tracers point both ways.

1246
02:08:42,190 --> 02:08:45,460
去檢查頂端的空間
Why don't you check the head space and she should run.

1247
02:08:53,870 --> 02:08:56,740
厄本，快點
Upham, hustle up!

1248
02:09:46,490 --> 02:09:50,390
厄本下士，這裡沒有30毫米口徑機槍
Corporal Upham. We don't have a.30 calibre machine gun here.

1249
02:09:50,590 --> 02:09:56,050
梅利西和鐘樓的傑克森才需要這個
Either Mister Mellish or Mr Jackson in the bell tower needs that.

1250
02:09:56,300 --> 02:09:59,360
厄本，傑克森有子彈，去拿給梅利西
Upham! Jackson's fine, turn around to Mellish!

1251
02:10:20,890 --> 02:10:24,620
有很多步兵，不知道會否上釣
There's a ton of infantry. I don't know if they took the bait, though.

1252
02:10:48,750 --> 02:10:51,020
還有口香糖嗎
Have you got any more of that?

1253
02:11:36,830 --> 02:11:39,060
裝甲車沒有上當
The Panzers didn't take the bait.

1254
02:11:44,110 --> 02:11:46,840
步兵團正向左進發
The infantry's moving to the left.

1255
02:11:47,040 --> 02:11:50,210
一輛裝甲車跟二十人剛剛開過
A half-track just went by with about 20 troops.

1256
02:13:29,210 --> 02:13:32,880
梅利西、漢德森，移位
Mellish, Henderson! Displace!

1257
02:13:54,000 --> 02:13:57,900
點火
Do it, now! Light it up! You! Light it!

1258
02:14:09,220 --> 02:14:13,590
右邊有三十人，設法阻截他們
30 infantry on the right flank. Get over there, find a hole and stop them!

1259
02:14:13,790 --> 02:14:16,260
移位
Displace!

1260
02:14:27,100 --> 02:14:28,870
厄本
Upham!

1261
02:14:43,640 --> 02:14:46,590
目標清除     去吧
- Clear! OK,   - Go!

1262
02:14:46,820 --> 02:14:48,550
德國人
Krauts!

1263
02:14:50,160 --> 02:14:52,390
向右邊進攻
Right flank!

1264
02:15:28,060 --> 02:15:30,920
伏下
Get down, get down!

1265
02:15:37,340 --> 02:15:40,460
厄本，30毫米口徑子彈
Upham! Thirty cal, hurry!

1266
02:15:40,670 --> 02:15:43,900
告訴上尉左翼快失守
Find the Captain, this flank's going to fold!

1267
02:16:38,890 --> 02:16:41,290
車子還在動
Traversing! He's still in this fight!

1268
02:16:42,800 --> 02:16:45,370
瑞恩，伏下
No! Ryan, get down, get down!

1269
