Ryan!

1270
02:17:18,730 --> 02:17:20,530
瑞恩
Ryan!

1271
02:17:21,830 --> 02:17:24,140
閉嘴     放開我
- Keep your mouth.   - Shut Get off me!

1272
02:17:24,350 --> 02:17:26,070
你沒事吧     放開我
- Are you alright?   - Get off of me!

1273
02:17:26,270 --> 02:17:28,740
上尉，我也沒事，謝謝
I'm fine too, Captain. Thanks.

1274
02:17:28,970 --> 02:17:33,440
夾擊他們，扔手榴彈過去
Hit them from both sides. Get aboard! Get a grenade in there!

1275
02:17:37,480 --> 02:17:38,920
手榴彈
Grenade!

1276
02:17:40,690 --> 02:17:43,620
是20毫米口徑機槍
20 mill! 20 mill!

1277
02:17:43,820 --> 02:17:45,480
是重型機槍，幹掉它
Flak gun, 20 mm. Take it out!

1278
02:17:58,940 --> 02:18:02,340
機槍給覆蓋著，打不到
Heavy weapon in defilade below! I ain't got a shot!

1279
02:18:06,880 --> 02:18:11,220
鉗子隊形，派克，目標在八點鐘方向
Pincer move! Parker! Targets eight o'clock, low!

1280
02:18:11,430 --> 02:18:13,510
願天主賜我力量
God grant me strength.

1281
02:18:26,970 --> 02:18:30,130
去吧，快移位
Let's go, displace! Come on!

1282
02:18:46,520 --> 02:18:49,720
厄本，躲好
Cover! Upham, cover!

1283
02:19:05,940 --> 02:19:08,000
30毫米子彈用光了
I'm out of.30 calibre.

1284
02:19:11,440 --> 02:19:13,970
天主賜我力量，教我的手打仗
Blessed be the Lord my strength, which teaches my hands to war

1285
02:19:14,210 --> 02:19:16,550
教我的指頭作戰
and my fingers to fight.

1286
02:19:25,160 --> 02:19:29,590
天主是我的堡壘、我的高塔和解脫者
My goodness and my fortress. My high tower and deliverer.

1287
02:19:33,000 --> 02:19:35,730
我的盾牌、我的依靠
My shield and He in whom I trust.

1288
02:19:39,310 --> 02:19:41,330
去吧，寶貝
Here you go, baby.

1289
02:20:03,930 --> 02:20:06,160
派克，伏下
Parker, get down!

1290
02:20:27,320 --> 02:20:29,620
上尉，那20毫米口徑手槍真要命
Captain, that 20 mm is killing us.

1291
02:20:29,820 --> 02:20:34,380
一定要毀掉它     我到上面去
- We've got to try to flank it somehow.   - Let me get over there for a top shot.

1292
02:20:59,620 --> 02:21:01,550
厄本
Upham!

1293
02:21:19,840 --> 02:21:24,710
厄本，拿子彈來
Upham, Upham! Upham, ammo, goddammit!

1294
02:22:07,820 --> 02:22:11,650
卡住了，拿30毫米子彈給我     用光了
- I'm jammed! Got any.30 calibre?   - I'm out.

1295
02:22:23,740 --> 02:22:26,170
厄本
Upham. Upham!

1296
02:23:18,860 --> 02:23:20,420
萊賓
Reiben!

1297
02:23:23,960 --> 02:23:25,160
萊賓
Reiben!

1298
02:23:52,320 --> 02:23:56,660
用光了，有人有子彈嗎
I'm out! I need another bandolier. Anybody got a bandolier?

1299
02:24:27,860 --> 02:24:29,920
混蛋
You piece of shit!

1300
02:25:14,470 --> 02:25:19,570
住手，聽我說，別這樣
Let's stop, let's stop! Listen to me! Stop! No, no, no...

1301
02:25:46,370 --> 02:25:48,130
該死
Fuck!

1302
02:25:55,980 --> 02:26:00,480
混蛋
Son of a bitch, son of a bitch!

1303
02:26:00,720 --> 02:26:02,810
混蛋
Son of a bitch!

1304
02:27:24,200 --> 02:27:28,610
用光了，那些60毫米炮彈
I'm out! Those.60 rounds...

1305
02:27:28,810 --> 02:27:31,670
沒有炮管也可以用     怎樣用
- We can use them without the tube.   - How?

1306
02:27:31,880 --> 02:27:35,140
這是引爆線，扔出去就行了
Fuse-arming wire, set back and heave it!

1307
02:27:50,460 --> 02:27:52,860
德國人
Panzer schreck!

1308
02:28:09,980 --> 02:28:11,970
去吧
Go, go!

1309
02:28:26,430 --> 02:28:28,960
到最後防線去
We're going to the Alamo.

1310
02:28:38,840 --> 02:28:41,110
最後防線
Alamo! Alamo!

1311
02:29:00,330 --> 02:29:03,820
交給我們，你們撤退     你跟著來
- We'll take it. You fall back!   - You be right behind us!

1312
02:29:04,070 --> 02:29:06,000
我們很快回來
As soon as we're in business.

1313
02:29:10,110 --> 02:29:12,540
萊賓，移位
Displace. Reiben!

1314
02:29:14,810 --> 02:29:16,840
裝彈
Reload!

1315
02:30:05,030 --> 02:30:06,500
開炮
Alright, go!

1316
02:30:07,670 --> 02:30:10,570
要炸橋了，快逃     快離開
- We're blowing the bridge! Get off!   - Off the bridge!

1317
02:30:34,660 --> 02:30:37,530
中士，麥克，你沒事吧
Sarge! Mike, are you alright?

1318
02:30:37,730 --> 02:30:40,130
我被風吹倒了     走吧
- I just got the wind knocked out of me.   - Let's go!

1319
02:30:40,330 --> 02:30:43,230
躲好，要炸橋了
Take cover, we're going to blow this bridge!

1320
02:30:45,170 --> 02:30:46,900
來吧
Come on!

1321
02:30:51,610 --> 02:30:53,940
虎式坦克要過橋了
Tiger company's coming across the bridge.

1322
02:31:26,680 --> 02:31:29,880
上尉，找個地方躲好
Captain, get behind something!

1323
02:31:55,710 --> 02:31:57,470
麥克
Mike!

1324
02:32:02,250 --> 02:32:04,010
麥克
Mike!

1325
02:32:46,490 --> 02:32:50,550
上尉，你去哪裡，回來
Captain, where the hell are you going? Captain, get back here!

1326
02:34:43,680 --> 02:34:45,110
厄本
Upham!

1327
02:35:14,770 --> 02:35:16,900
堅持住
Hang in there.

1328
02:36:02,290 --> 02:36:04,260
救護員
Medic!

1329
02:36:06,860 --> 02:36:09,520
有救護員嗎
Medic! We've got a medic?

1330
02:36:16,170 --> 02:36:19,860
是P-51反坦克攻擊機
They're tankbusters, sir. P-51s.

1331
02:36:20,070 --> 02:36:22,160
我們的守護天使
Angels on our shoulders.

1332
02:36:28,180 --> 02:36:30,270
什麼事
What, sir?

1333
02:36:34,320 --> 02:36:36,380
詹姆斯
James...

1334
02:36:37,620 --> 02:36:39,750
別辜負
Earn this.

1335
02:36:43,330 --> 02:36:45,690
別辜負大家
Earn it.

1336
02:37:14,100 --> 02:37:16,850
“親愛的瑞恩太太”
"My dear Mrs Ryan."

1337
02:37:17,500 --> 02:37:21,560
“我有個喜訊要帶給你”
"It's with a profound sense of joy that I write to inform you"

1338
02:37:21,670 --> 02:37:26,410
“就是令郞二等兵詹姆斯·瑞恩安然無恙”
"that your son, Private James Ryan, is well"

1339
02:37:26,510 --> 02:37:30,890
“現在正從歐洲的戰線回國”
"and at this moment on his way home from European battlefields."

1340
02:37:31,280 --> 02:37:35,440
“詹姆斯盡忠職守”
"Reports indicate that James did his duty in combat"

1341
02:37:35,600 --> 02:37:38,540
“勇氣過人、堅毅不屈”
"with great courage and steadfast dedication"

1342
02:37:38,850 --> 02:37:43,410
“縱使他得知兄弟陣亡”
"even after he was informed of the loss your family has suffered"

1343
02:37:43,640 --> 02:37:48,280
“仍堅持參與這場剷除獨裁暴政的偉大戰爭”
"in this great campaign to rid the world of tyranny and oppression."

1344
02:37:48,690 --> 02:37:51,790
“我與戰爭部長”
"I take great pleasure injoining the Secretary of War"

1345
02:37:51,990 --> 02:37:56,800
“美軍同仁及美國國民”
"the men and women of the US Army, and the citizens of a grateful nation"

1346
02:37:56,860 --> 02:38:02,750
“僅此祝你身體健康，與詹姆斯一起活得愉快”
"in wishing you good health and many years of happiness with James."

1347
02:38:03,310 --> 02:38:07,770
“雖然愛子平安歸國”
"Nothing, not even the safe return of a beloved son"

1348
02:38:08,110 --> 02:38:12,140
“也無法彌補你和千千萬萬個美國家庭”
"can compensate you or the thousands of other American families"

1349
02:38:12,360 --> 02:38:15,430
“在戰爭中遭受的創痛”
"who have suffered great loss in this tragic war."

1350
02:38:15,750 --> 02:38:17,870
“我想與你分享”
"I might share with you some words"

1351
02:38:17,970 --> 02:38:23,320
“一番在悲痛絕望中支援著我的說話”
"which have sustained me through nights of peril, loss and heartache"

1352
02:38:23,730 --> 02:38:27,990
“是這樣的一番說話”
"and I quote, 'I pray that our heavenly Father"

1353
02:38:28,070 --> 02:38:31,100
“願天主安撫你的喪子之痛”
"may assuage the anguish of your bereavement"

1354
02:38:31,380 --> 02:38:35,240
“讓你永遠懷念遠去的摯愛”
"and leave you only the cherished memory of the loved and lost"

1355
02:38:35,470 --> 02:38:37,710
“神聖的榮耀都歸於你們”
"and the solemn pride that must be yours"

1356
02:38:37,910 --> 02:38:43,180
“因你們為自由付出了重大的代價”
"to have laid a so costly a sacrifice upon the altar of freedom."

1357
02:38:43,450 --> 02:38:45,350
“林肯敬上”
"Abraham Lincoln."

1358
02:38:45,660 --> 02:38:48,050
“深表敬意”
"Yours very sincerely and respectfully"

1359
02:38:48,290 --> 02:38:51,920
“參謀長馬歇爾上將”
"George C. Marshall. General, Chief of Staff."

1360
02:39:42,830 --> 02:39:48,280
今天我家人也來了，他們想跟我來
My family is with me today. They wanted to come with me.

1361
02:39:50,960 --> 02:39:56,120
說真的，我不知道到這裡來會有什麼感受
To be honest with you, I wasn't sure how I would feel coming back here.

1362
02:39:58,530 --> 02:40:04,480
我每天都想著當日你在橋上說的話
Every day, I think about what you said to me that day on the bridge.

1363
02:40:06,130 --> 02:40:10,330
我努力活好每一天
I've tried to live my life the best I could.

1364
02:40:10,630 --> 02:40:13,360
希望這已經足夠
I hope that was enough.

1365
02:40:13,890 --> 02:40:17,670
希望這至少讓你覺得
I hope that at least in your eyes...

1366
02:40:18,410 --> 02:40:22,270
我沒有辜負你們為我做的一切
l've earned what all of you have done for me.

1367
02:40:35,710 --> 02:40:37,230
詹姆斯
James.

1368
02:40:39,220 --> 02:40:41,990
“約翰米勒上尉”
"Captain John H. Miller."

1369
02:40:49,980 --> 02:40:54,590
跟我說我這輩子沒白活     什麼
- Tell me I have led a good life.   - What?

1370
02:40:55,160 --> 02:40:57,410
跟我說，我是個好人
Tell me I'm a good mess.

1371
02:41:04,520 --> 02:41:06,480
你是個好人
You are.

1372
02:42:01,040 --> 02:42:07,570
